{"word":"G518 - ἀπαγγέλλω - apangéllō - ap-ang-el'-lo - Bring word","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπαγγέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apangéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ang-el'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring word</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அறிவி, அறிக்கையிடு, சொல்லு"},{"paragraph":"1. to bring tidings (from a person or thing), bring word, report"},{"paragraph":"2. to proclaim"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G32 - ἄγγελος - ángelos - ang'-el-os/32\">G32</a>; to <i>announce:</i> - bring word (again), declare, report, shew (again), tell.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1229/1229\">G1229</a>, <a href=\"#/G1804/1804\">G1804</a>, <a href=\"#/G2604/2604\">G2604</a>, <a href=\"#/G2605/2605\">G2605</a>, <a href=\"#/G31/31\">G31</a>, <a href=\"#/G312/312\">G312</a>, <a href=\"#/G4293/4293\">G4293</a>, <a href=\"#/G518/518\">G518</a>"}]}